bgm.name: ダンジョン19(静寂に潜む闇)171007_95bpm

parameters.name: 探索15(セキュリティホール)

parameters:
\n<Ladro>As usual, those guys up there are slowpokes. Well, I've got
my livelihood on the line here-. Today's haul is pretty good
too~♪
\n<Katara>Hm, so this is your so-called secret base? A warehouse?
\n<Katara>Hm, so this is your hideout, huh? Looks like a warehouse.

\n<Katara>What do you say at times like this? Forgive me! No, not
that... be remorseful... right?

\n<Katara>You shouldn't lick a cat's paw. Besides, I have the blessing
of the wind. When it comes to racing, I won't lose to
anyone.

\n<Ladro>...(Huh? They haven't noticed? Then, there's still a chance
to handle this.)

\n<Ladro>Hehehe. You seem confident in your agility. But this is my
home ground.

\n<Ladro>I've thought of every possibility and set traps all over the
place. Right at your feet too!

\n<Ladro>That glue trap is strong. It seems agility was your forte,
but now that's become meaningless. Do you have any other
strengths? Huh?
\n<Ladro>What?! It's so sticky...! I can't move...
\n<Ladro>Kyaaahhh! Don't look! Don't look at me-!!!
\n<Ladro>Hey, you pervert kid! Don't look this way!

\n<Ladro>...(Huh? What's that? It's getting bigger? Is Katara... a
futanari?)

\n<Ladro>...(Huh? That's... swelling up... Could this be... an
opportunity?)

\n<Ladro>Fu...♥ I see. I've found your weakness. Now it's my turn to
corner you.

\n<Ladro>(I can't afford to lose. It's not like I have anything to
lose. Time to cast aside my shame, Ladro!)
